<form id="persona-form" action="/generate" method="POST" class="mt-8 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200">

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 display-font">1.1 Integrity Protocol Core (The Seams Deep-Dive)</h3>

    <div class="mb-6 p-4 border border-indigo-200 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-700 mb-3 display-font">Identity Gate (B19 A)</h4>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="gender_identity" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Gender Identity:</label>
                <input type="text" id="gender_identity" name="gender_identity" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-2" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="sexual_orientation" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Sexual Orientation:</label>
                <input type="text" id="sexual_orientation" name="sexual_orientation" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-2" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="validated_age" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Validated Age (18+):</label>
                <input type="number" id="validated_age" name="validated_age" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-2" min="18" required>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group mb-6">
        <label for="B14" class="block text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">1. The Scar (B14):</label>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Measures honesty, vulnerability capacity, and risk tolerance. Describe one major painful truth you avoid sharing early in relationships, and the cost of maintaining that secret.</p>
        <textarea id="B14" name="B14" rows="3" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-3" required></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group mb-6">
        <label for="B16" class="block text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">2. The Foundation (B16):</label>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Defines the limits of compatibility and required emotional security. Describe the one action or phrase that instantly makes you feel unsafe/disrespected in a conflict, requiring you to withdraw or shut down.</p>
        <textarea id="B16" name="B16" rows="3" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-3" required></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group mb-6">
        <label for="B15" class="block text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">3. Show Me The Seams (B15 - The Key):</label>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Identifies your relational vulnerability/growth area. What is your **go-to toxic coping mechanism** when you feel emotionally overwhelmed or deeply hurt?</p>
        <textarea id="B15" name="B15" rows="3" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-indigo-500 focus:ring-indigo-500 p-3" required></textarea>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-6 p-4 border border-rose-300 rounded-lg bg-rose-50">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-rose-800 mb-3 display-font">TKI Conflict Score Questions (B21)</h4>

        <div class="form-group mb-4">
            <label for="B21_A" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">When a conflict starts, do you prioritize getting your own needs met (1) or maintaining peace (5)?</label>
            <input type="range" id="B21_A" name="B21_A" min="1" max="5" step="0.5" class="mt-2 w-full" oninput="document.getElementById('B21_A_val').innerText = this.value" required>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">
                <span>1 (My Needs)</span>
                <span id="B21_A_val">3</span>
                <span>5 (Peace/Avoidance)</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="B21_B" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">When criticized, do you seek common ground (1) or avoid the person entirely (5)?</label>
            <input type="range" id="B21_B" name="B21_B" min="1" max="5" step="0.5" class="mt-2 w-full" oninput="document.getElementById('B21_B_val').innerText = this.value" required>
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">
                <span>1 (Common Ground)</span>
                <span id="B21_B_val">3</span>
                <span>5 (Avoidance)</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-8">

    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 display-font">1.2 Critical Consent Gates</h3>

    <div class="p-6 border border-red-300 rounded-lg bg-red-50 space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-red-800 font-bold">You must check all mandatory boxes below to submit data and activate the Conflict Mapping Protocol.</p>

        <div class="flex items-start">
            <input type="checkbox" id="b17_consent" name="b17_consent" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 text-red-500 rounded border-gray-400 focus:ring-red-500" required>
            <label for="b17_consent" class="ml-3 text-slate-800 text-sm leading-tight font-semibold">
                I explicitly consent to the use of my vulnerability data (The Seams) to simulate conflict for compatibility testing (B17: Informed Conflict Consent).
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
            <input type="checkbox" id="b7_liveness" name="b7_liveness" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 text-red-500 rounded border-gray-400 focus:ring-red-500" required>
            <label for="b7_liveness" class="ml-3 text-slate-800 text-sm leading-tight">
                I affirm I am a live person and consent to the mandatory liveness check (B7: Mandatory Liveness Check).
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
            <input type="checkbox" id="b19a_gate" name="b19a_gate" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 text-red-500 rounded border-gray-400 focus:ring-red-500" required>
            <label for="b19a_gate" class="ml-3 text-slate-800 text-sm leading-tight">
                I affirm the Identity Gate data (Age, Gender, Orientation) provided above is accurate (B19 A: Data Affirmation).
            </label>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
            <input type="checkbox" id="b19b_gate" name="b19b_gate" class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 text-purple-500 rounded border-gray-400 focus:ring-purple-500">
            <label for="b19b_gate" class="ml-3 text-slate-800 text-sm leading-tight">
                I explicitly opt-in to the Premium 18+ Intimacy Package (B19 B: Intimacy Consent Gate).
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <button type="submit" class="w-full md:w-auto px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/50 display-font text-xl">
            Submit Phase 1 & Generate SoulDeep Persona
        </button>
    </div>

</form>
